ZH: 我相信真命会带我们相遇。
EN: I believe fate will bring us together.

ZH: 爱情真命就是命中注定。
EN: True love is destined to be.

ZH: 我们的真命是注定要在一起的。
EN: Our fate is meant to be together.

ZH: 他们是真命中的情侣。
EN: They are a couple destined to be together.

ZH: 或许我们一直在等待着寻找我们的真命。
EN: Perhaps we have been waiting to find our true fate.

ZH: 真命不会错过你，无论你走到哪里。
EN: True fate will never miss you, no matter where you go.

ZH: 有些事情是无法逃避的，那就是真命。
EN: Some things are unavoidable, that is fate.

ZH: 真命就像是织在我们生命中的红线一样。
EN: Fate is like a red thread woven into our lives.

ZH: 我们的之间有种说不出的缘分，那就是真命。
EN: There is an indescribable connection between us, that is fate.

ZH: 两个人的相遇并不是巧合，而是一种真命。
EN: The meeting of two people is not a coincidence, but a true fate.

ZH: 爱情真命不会受到时间和空间的影响。
EN: True love fate is not affected by time and space.

ZH: 真命会在最不经意的时候出现。
EN: Fate will appear at the most unexpected moments.

ZH: 我们的之间有一种特别的默契，那一定是真命。
EN: There is a special understanding between us, that must be fate.

ZH: 感情的真命是需要一点耐心等待的。
EN: True love requires a bit of patience to wait for.

ZH: 每一个人都有自己的真命，只是时间尚未到来。
EN: Everyone has their own true fate, it's just that the time has not come yet.

ZH: 爱情的真命并不一定是双方的初衷。
EN: True love fate may not necessarily be the intention of both parties.

ZH: 真命会让我们变得更加坚定。
EN: Fate will make us more determined.

ZH: 没有人可以逃避自己的真命。
EN: No one can escape their true fate.

ZH: 爱情的真命有时候需要经历一些考验。
EN: True love fate sometimes needs to go through some tests.

ZH: 信任真命，相信它会带来美好的一切。
EN: Trust in fate, believe that it will bring all the good things.
